}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "EWW302-A1-BL-015" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. {{See also|Linksys E5400|Wistron NeWeb}} *{{WiFiCert|WFA81722|01/25/2019}} {{FCC ST|08/01/2019}}
We are guessing that the maximum link rate for 5GHz 802.11ac has been :reduced from 867Mbps to 650Mbps by disabling 256QAM support.
All of the following devices are internally identical: * [[Linksys E5400]] - ''AC1200 Dual-Band WiFi Router'' * [[Linksys E5350]] - ''AC1000 Dual-Band WiFi Router'' * [[Linksys E5300]] - ''AC750 Dual-Band WiFi Router'' * [[Linksys E2500 v4]] - ''N600 Dual-Band WiFi Router''
